data.description: Welcome to this lakefront residence nestled in the charming Lake St. Clair subdivision! This beautiful home boasts three bedrooms, three full bathrooms, a convenient two-car garage, and an expansive three-car-wide driveway, ideally suited for accommodating your boat! Step out to the back, where you'll find a generous 10' x 22' deck, providing the perfect spot to unwind and soak in the picturesque lake views. The walk-out basement opens up to a fenced-in yard, all situated on a prime lakefront lot along the serene Lake 2 within the Lake St. Clair community.
